  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >On mysterious Box Island, ancient ruins hold puzzle-filled challenges. Move crates to targets across 500+ maze levels to unlock island secrets. Young adventurers await in this crate-pushing odyssey!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >More than 500 challenging levels</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A variety of different level designs, ranging from easy to difficult, allowing players to gradually master the game skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3646430/extras/26b9e0cf1550577e55561a0e148185b2.avif?t=1774439726\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3646430/extras_big/26b9e0cf1550577e55561a0e148185b2.avif?t=1774439726 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Level Replay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each level you have played has a replay function to help you study the optimal solution.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3646430/extras/4e25d68dc8696f8b00268c9b4b95ee7a.avif?t=1774439726\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3646430/extras_big/4e25d68dc8696f8b00268c9b4b95ee7a.avif?t=1774439726 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >RPG elements</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Traditional gameplay combined with RPG elements, NPC will explore the mysterious box island with you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3646430/extras/6df91f586968e4a18b3baf4ce5c6ea78.avif?t=1774439726\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3646430/extras_big/6df91f586968e4a18b3baf4ce5c6ea78.avif?t=1774439726 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3646430/extras/b8ca08d3aef00dabd9daed1d578bf5f1.avif?t=1774439726\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3646430/extras_big/b8ca08d3aef00dabd9daed1d578bf5f1.avif?t=1774439726 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >On mysterious Box Island, ancient ruins hold puzzle-filled challenges. Move crates to targets across 500+ maze levels to unlock island secrets. Young adventurers await in this crate-pushing odyssey!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >More than 500 challenging levels</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A variety of different level designs, ranging from easy to difficult, allowing players to gradually master the game skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3646430/extras/26b9e0cf1550577e55561a0e148185b2.avif?t=1774439726\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3646430/extras_big/26b9e0cf1550577e55561a0e148185b2.avif?t=1774439726 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Level Replay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each level you have played has a replay function to help you study the optimal solution.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3646430/extras/4e25d68dc8696f8b00268c9b4b95ee7a.avif?t=1774439726\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3646430/extras_big/4e25d68dc8696f8b00268c9b4b95ee7a.avif?t=1774439726 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >RPG elements</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Traditional gameplay combined with RPG elements, NPC will explore the mysterious box island with you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3646430/extras/6df91f586968e4a18b3baf4ce5c6ea78.avif?t=1774439726\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3646430/extras_b